{"tid":1489113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Facebook 同Twitter 都話中共利用社交媒體針對香港發放假消息","createTime":"2019-08-19T19:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T11:04:07.000Z","uid":213062,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0aab2e9ce31644997bb47673972863cb0d6f48","tid":1489113,"uid":213062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:55:18.000Z","msg":"紐約時報報導Facebook 同twitter 都發現同封鎖左大批源自中國嘅帳戶 ，話呢d 帳戶不斷散播香港示威嘅假消息。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 更加係有中共媒體利用佢地嘅平台不斷散播香港示威者「暴力」行為同受「外國勢力」操控嘅資訊之後，禁止佢地係Twitter 落廣告。Twitter 批評，話唔會容許呢d 秘密，操縱嘅行為出現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人必自侮而後人侮之<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，文宣全力煲大佢！<br />\n<br />\n全文Link: <strong>The New York Times: Facebook and Twitter Say China Is Spreading Disinformation in Hong Kong </strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/19/technology/hong-kong-protests-china-disinformation-facebook-twitter.html?smid=fb-nytimes&amp;smtyp=cur&amp;fbclid=IwAR3VX0L8MBAnrbeXh0UJFjS-VqcNedJIiCIpTQqpGkyjHPP-fmx2b1D9uLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F08%2F19%2Ftechnology%2Fhong-kong-protests-china-disinformation-facebook-twitter.html%3Fsmid%3Dfb-nytimes%26smtyp%3Dcur%26fbclid%3DIwAR3VX0L8MBAnrbeXh0UJFjS-VqcNedJIiCIpTQqpGkyjHPP-fmx2b1D9uLw&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=372b2ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/08/19/technology/hong-kong-protests-china-disinformation-facebook-twitter.html?smid=fb-nytimes&amp;smtyp=cur&amp;fbclid=IwAR3VX0L8MBAnrbeXh0UJFjS-VqcNedJIiCIpTQqpGkyjHPP-fmx2b1D9uLw</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個Post 都有講<br />\nTwitter官方證實中共國家級力量帶風向！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489036\" data-auto-link target=\"_bl